                    tradeTableRow(["2026 JPY Trade", "JPY / FXY", "Watch / staged cash", "Wait", "JPY can weaken further toward 162 while Fed stays hawkish and BOJ remains unclear; watch JGBs first."], widths: [1.3, 0.75, 1.3, 1.1, 1.5])
