                    tradeTableRow(["Fertilizer producers", "NTR, CF, MOS", "Primary equity expression. NTR is broad fertilizer/ag retail; CF is nitrogen and cheap-US-gas leverage; MOS is phosphate/potash and more cyclical."], widths: [1.0, 1.8, 2.7])
