                    tradeTableRow(["Stage 1", "Fertilizer stress confirms: urea/ammonia/phosphate elevated, NTR/CF/MOS/MOO hold higher lows.", "Starter basket only, preferably on pullback. No grain chase yet."], widths: [0.9, 2.3, 2.3])
