                    tradeTableRow(["Stage 4", "Policy response: export controls, subsidies, fertilizer restrictions, price caps, or tariff shifts.", "Reduce if policy caps upside; add only if policy worsens scarcity."], widths: [0.9, 2.3, 2.3])
