                    id: "adhoc.1211.2026-05-03",
                    title: "IRC Analysis: BYD Q1 pullback, margin pressure and trading levels",
                    source: "Codex ad hoc research",
                    dateText: "2026-05-03",
                    markdown: """
                    ## BYD 1211.HK - Pullback Analysis

                    **Price context:** IB Gateway historical bars showed BYD closed at **HK$102.50 on 2026-04-30**, down about **9.5%** from the 60-day closing high of HK$113.20 on 2026-04-16, but still up about 3.4% over the 6-month IB sample.

